CSTutor.Model.Tutorial

Class TutorialPage

  • java.lang.Object
    • CSTutor.Model.Tutorial.TutorialPage

  • public class TutorialPage
extends java.lang.Object
    A Student page is an individual topic page within a tutorial track. This is the page that students interact with to take the tutorials on.
